graduates.name: Preston Ware
graduates.body1: Hey there, welcome to my page. Im definitely the coolest graduate, you can't deny that. Throughout my time here at DB I took 3 years of coding classes. Those classes consisted of Mobile App Development, Computer Science Principles 2 (I Skipped the first one), and Coding Practicum, all for a whole year. Out of the 3 classes that I took, as a senior I definitely believe that Coding Practicum was the best. I was assigned tasks every day including running around the school to do assignments or pick up some tech for Mr. Bailey.
